{"tid":1661793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"721係黑警春袋","createTime":"2019-10-18T10:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T13:03:33.000Z","uid":69277,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"71371888a46a2d48f85ebdf97229c1a8dd91aff9","tid":1661793,"uid":69277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T10:39:46.000Z","msg":"就嚟三個月，有無一件死黑警停職？<br />\n游乃強、李漢文、鄧炳強，呢班仆街仲喺度風流快活。<br />\n就嚟三個月，打立場姐姐條契弟畀人拉咗未？<br />\n<br />\n831、陳彥霖、開槍殺健仔等等等等唔係唔理，<br />\n只係有個春袋喺手，我哋無理由放過，或者將佢排喺個list嘅最後。<br />\n<br />\n清算狗隊，由721開始。<br />\n<br />\n10.20 九龍見<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f567fda7ce5410df649d8e5cd67a90344c12c6","tid":1661793,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T10:40:25.000Z","msg":"721唔見人 <br />\n831打死人<br />\n10月1 射鳩人"},{"pid":"8602758cc6a97f82b1631de8b8bb944403015351","tid":1661793,"uid":69277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T10:41:04.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n721 1020 721 1020"},{"pid":"8972d8466f35816771b9a26116821dc075d4f43f","tid":1661793,"uid":222970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T10:41:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>放心 等到我地連登仔80幾歲果陣都會日日提721 叫埋個孫 太孫勿忘721 睇黎政府只可以用焚書坑儒先可以抹走721歷史上最黑暗既一日</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"b5d31b551076ba74403f4365512ad8ee3405f276","tid":1661793,"uid":48427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T10:42:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a6488f5b7b8a547